---
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="section-label reveal">About</div>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">
          Engineer by practice,<br />problem-solver by nature.
        </h2>
        <div class="about-body reveal">
          <p>
            I'm Jeff — a developer and infrastructure engineer who got hooked on
            building things that work reliably. What started as curiosity about how
            systems fit together turned into a goal of building platforms that teams
            and businesses can depend on.
          </p>
          <p>
            My approach is deliberate: understand the problem deeply before writing
            a line of code. I work across the full stack — from container orchestration
            and reverse proxies to clean front-end interfaces — but my real value is
            in making complex systems simple enough that someone else can maintain them.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not building production systems, I'm running a home lab where I
            prototype, break things safely, and stay sharp on emerging tools. Every
            solution I ship has been battle-tested first.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-details reveal">
        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Core Stack</h3>
          <ul class="tag-list">
            <li>Linux / Ubuntu</li>
            <li>Podman / Docker</li>
            <li>Traefik</li>
            <li>Prometheus / Grafana</li>
            <li>TypeScript / Node.js</li>
            <li>Python</li>
            <li>Bash / Automation</li>
            <li>Git / CI-CD</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-card">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Interests</h3>
          <ul class="tag-list muted">
            <li>Self-hosted platforms</li>
            <li>Infrastructure as Code</li>
            <li>Observability</li>
            <li>AI-assisted development</li>
            <li>Network architecture</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-body p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .about-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .detail-card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: border-color var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .detail-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }

  .detail-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .tag-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .tag-list li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79, 143, 234, 0.15);
  }

  .tag-list.muted li {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border-color: var(--border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
